<i>noun</i>: 합법화 [합뻐퐈], 법제화 [법쩨화] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>합법화 [합뻐퐈]</dt><br>
<dd>legalization; legitimization</dd><br>
<dd>법과 규범에 맞도록 함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of recognizing something as in accordance with law and rule.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>법제화 [법쩨화]</dt><br>
<dd>legislation; legalization; enactment</dd><br>
<dd>법으로 정해 놓음.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of making a law.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>